{"tid":590404,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現原來自己都幾廢","createTime":"2018-03-12T14:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T18:51:41.000Z","uid":5065,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"83de50ce3c22752bb4f434deb2e2d518816f67ae","tid":590404,"uid":5065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"上吊嗰一刻明明已經放鬆晒成個人，但臨到無意識嗰一吓又無勇氣繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我真係受夠呢一兩年咁多嘢壓上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但一個廢柴要死真係唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e19f2d783a76d8ec4823d75748dfad27f3eb42b","tid":590404,"uid":173542,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好放棄"},{"pid":"6221e0e623c23b1b9d8d28e268ecb724f5342621","tid":590404,"uid":5065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e19f2d783a76d8ec4823d75748dfad27f3eb42b","tid":590404,"uid":173542,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:49:13.000Z","msg":"加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好放棄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:51:06.000Z","msg":"無晒油嘅時候真係諗唔到下一步可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友、家人，根本無一個可以吐苦水，有咩都要自己受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59cff75cde307394cd4182ccee09879995cbcc80","tid":590404,"uid":173542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"不如講吓發生咩事？"},{"pid":"b95fe10b5ce40b358ce855442ee03d7be5181625","tid":590404,"uid":142378,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"巴打發生咩事啊"},{"pid":"18dd876662f4d66506847069d0c19c172ee0d3bc","tid":590404,"uid":5065,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"59cff75cde307394cd4182ccee09879995cbcc80","tid":590404,"uid":173542,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"不如講吓發生咩事？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:04:18.000Z","msg":"識咗咁多朋友，好多so call叫做中學識到依家，但發現自己完全無一個可以信任到咩都講出口，一直以嚟只有我聽佢哋講，做佢哋嘅樹窿。<br />\n<br />\n到咗垃圾HD又無乜朋友，只有一個異性知己，可惜自卑心作祟，好想親近多啲、依靠佢多啲，但明知人哋有男朋友都仲癡心妄想可以一世做朋友。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，因為對方喺學校有自己朋友圈、我又完全無辦法融入。唔想打擾之下想自己走開，又發現原來一早已經依賴晒佢，唔係話走就走。一諗起自己遲早要走就好揪心。<br />\n<br />\n到近嚟見到個個有interview call，自己乜柒都無，日日都提心吊膽，好驚白費兩年時間。仲未計屋企平時都要唔多唔少幫補吓，如果就咁浪費兩年真係唔知點樣交代。<br />\n<br />\n好似完全睇唔到將來咁樣。無論邊個都吐唔到苦水，每日都喺度諗我到底為咩而存在。"},{"pid":"97d230ac608ad6b59c91d900527c9c4ce87f8403","tid":590404,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"你比太大壓力自己啦"},{"pid":"db0853d918a21e201f4a9ad02d7050d364d2053a","tid":590404,"uid":4655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97d230ac608ad6b59c91d900527c9c4ce87f8403","tid":590404,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"你比太大壓力自己啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"船到橋頭自然直<br />\n巴打，珍惜生命。"},{"pid":"8f94fd5b4ab910501adaab0b610925782c120906","tid":590404,"uid":171816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:12:37.000Z","msg":"This is life bro."},{"pid":"48831bd691498387986469b5a841c45ac8310c95","tid":590404,"uid":5065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db0853d918a21e201f4a9ad02d7050d364d2053a","tid":590404,"uid":4655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"97d230ac608ad6b59c91d900527c9c4ce87f8403","tid":590404,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"你比太大壓力自己啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:11:16.000Z","msg":"船到橋頭自然直<br />\n巴打，珍惜生命。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"身邊個個都覺得我mental health，連我自己都有咁樣說服過自己可以好快無嘢，但發覺一直以嚟真係佢哋覺得，自己其實懦弱到不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b447bc2d50731f779a0ebd4bc2742809cddcde","tid":590404,"uid"